msgid ""
"The module supports new :mod:`~stat.ST_MODE` flags, :mod:`~stat.S_IFDOOR`, :"
"attr:`~stat.S_IFPORT`, and :attr:`~stat.S_IFWHT`.  (Contributed by Christian "
